{"title":"Leucemia mieloide crónica","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Hematología/Paper. Leucemia mieloide crónica-2025-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"LEUCEMIA MIELOIDE CRÓNICA:\\NACTUALIZACIÓN 2025","guid":"r4iDjTqYViiGxYB5K1gQDg","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"## DESCRIPCIÓN GENERAL\\NDE LA ENFERMEDAD","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"- Neoplasia mieloproliferativa con incidencia anual de 2 casos/100,000","guid":"KdkdrN-mMHjlKtM81Eri9w","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"- Representa aproximadamente 15% de nuevos casos de leucemia en adultos","guid":"5B6Me4tAr3TlaPUcP4J90A","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"- Estimación de 9280 nuevos casos en EE.UU. en 2024","guid":"ZZKDY_K4CtgXTSOzE6thyQ","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"- Mortalidad anual reducida de 10-20% a 1-2% desde introducción de imatinib (2000)","guid":"IQksDe8df4gPGWNub7J1qg","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"- Prevalencia aumentada de 30,000 casos (2000) a 150, 000+ casos (2024)","guid":"n4VJEDbWh-QTX8RNGQIVzw","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"- Prevalencia proyectada: 400-450,000 casos en EE.UU. para 2040-2050","guid":"EufRvkZXtsJEBmHFULmXOQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"0","text":"## DIAGNÓSTICO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"- Caracterizada por translocación genética balanceada t(9;22)(q34;q11.2)","guid":"A28YpRNvQo6moG6NWbwVDQ","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"- Fusión del gen ABL1 (cromosoma 9q34) con el gen BCR (cromosoma 22q11.2)","guid":"lw7SQXwt-khkJkdhwpjMpA","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"8","text":"- Conocido como cromosoma Filadelfia","guid":"wE96eUsSM68WSv7_SOgASg","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"8","text":"- Consecuencia molecular: generación del oncogén BCR::ABL1","guid":"fUsADlatEjCuBj8HFdzIVg","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"8","text":"- Resultado: traducción en oncoproteína BCR::ABL1","guid":"cg3HIx2lVHy9F04fOXE63g","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"8","text":"- Métodos\\Ndiagnósticos:","guid":"TU4sWEaJ-8xI7PwMnfKKwA","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"- Citogenética convencional (cariotipo)","guid":"m36ze1JV_5g4YIYzfYeZbQ","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"- Hibridación fluorescente in situ (FISH)","guid":"pOu_iG-tTbvmu2QU5rmUgA","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"- PCR cualitativa y cuantitativa (RT-PCR)","guid":"9Xxt_m0rehcTG3In_STbcQ","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"14","text":"- PCR digital de gotas (ddPCR)","guid":"OF-KQeVXAQ_H-f1S2UoVAQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"8","text":"- Aspirado medular: requerido para diagnóstico y estadificación","guid":"PLDnl6tq5WFDZoAxSq7_3A","children":[]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"0","text":"## MANIFESTACIONES Y\\NESTADIFICACIÓN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"- 50% de pacientes son asintomáticos al diagnóstico","guid":"YtbZOVxdY0X9lH9PRVJYiA","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"- Tres fases:","guid":"P7LNH3qx5G-ZOYrkm3VzwA","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"- Fase crónica (FC): 90-95% de presentación","guid":"75cgq9BjfOGRIhtRQvi28Q","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"- Fase acelerada (FA)","guid":"2CNMbgCfwiwpS1_QII5Buw","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"22","text":"- Fase blástica (FB)","guid":"7shPGyOD7jTmK1S2n5pLzg","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"20","text":"- Síntomas comunes:","guid":"PRuMa8A3M7-RAKiKz-VUEA","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"- Fatiga, pérdida de peso, malestar, saciedad temprana","guid":"dogwEcs4iaZuNVMvGdIKrw","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"- Dolor abdominal por esplenomegalia","guid":"qfLKEuWsGfi6WY0q_EUTlg","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"20","text":"- Esplenomegalia: signo físico más constante (20-40% de pacientes)","guid":"gbr1MlXups0l7SlMd5i3sQ","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"20","text":"- Hepatomegalia: menos común (5-10%)","guid":"EkrvryGdrycQTxzyC9E-vw","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"0","text":"## TERAPIA DE\\NPRIMERA LÍNEA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"- Inhibidores de tirosina quinasa (ITQ)\\Naprobados:","guid":"NSKrk8mByNO5c6tWB5XvCA","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"- Imatinib (primer ITQ aprobado por FDA)","guid":"z5T4O-k8emi7Jlojfmfx2g","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"- Dasatinib","guid":"pHkE4tZWo_eRROrfv3UldQ","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"- Bosutinib","guid":"dYS2UZ6RzM70smKSZMG3lw","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"32","text":"- Nilotinib","guid":"stMWX0lFdvmt-j-CEwMXSw","children":[]}]},{"id":"37","parent":"31","text":"- Eficacia probada:","guid":"IEBXJa85SONfAIcGz1q_tQ","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"- Imatinib: supervivencia general a 10 años de 83.3%","guid":"T9pIVltvlDz3Yx_iOhSx3A","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"- Respuesta citogenética completa acumulada: 83%","guid":"DQUS_Ka4S8W_ktYtiH4GuA","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"- Respuesta molecular mayor a 10 años: 93%","guid":"ovhHcdHMIkO7hkrFtQTprw","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"31","text":"- ITQ de segunda\\Ngeneración:","guid":"-ojzN2ZbdgClQnmsLr2Jzw","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"- Respuestas más rápidas y profundas que imatinib","guid":"cdtFBpC0dBpGkaZ9UK3C3Q","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"41","text":"- Sin impacto en supervivencia a largo plazo","guid":"wcQnc4oekOjIe11nOCHykQ","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"- Mayor tasa de eventos adversos","guid":"XF5nzcaW7rp5yxrJq9vqOA","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"31","text":"- Opciones de dosis\\Noptimizadas:","guid":"aj2W8lYEGVuLnZxn0YgCgQ","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"- Dasatinib 50 mg diario: eficacia similar y menor toxicidad que 100 mg diario","guid":"9tP-M2MXcyJsBoH9wc8IGw","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"45","text":"- Dasatinib 20 mg diario: opción viable para pacientes mayores (>70 años)","guid":"ZHBeuZa1-lGD_6fRgPNDxg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"0","text":"## TERAPIA DE\\NRESCATE","guid":"","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"- Opciones para fallo de\\Nterapia de primera línea:","guid":"Y2fp59pXVJLMGXifeI7Nhg","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"- ITQ de segunda y tercera generación","guid":"QTqSQ0M3BvXFV9nAeC9Geg","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"48","text":"- Para mutación T315I: ponatinib, asciminib y olverembatinib","guid":"kT4WpVtoavv21UF1XOBBGg","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"48","text":"- Trasplante alogénico\\Nde células madre:","guid":"Ss9cRdTZnuHEed_gMqnvGg","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"- Opción importante para pacientes con FC-LMC y fallo (resistencia) a al menos dos ITQ","guid":"FwH_oGtOqMOvMS5QqY9fTw","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"- Para todos los pacientes en fase avanzada","guid":"e0me6STZ_cAfYw4VPtZkDg","children":[]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"48","text":"- Opciones para recaída\\Ncitogenética post-fallo:","guid":"ugKM7tokpsMFdIh_jp2PrA","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"- Continuar ITQ diario más efectivo/menos tóxico","guid":"J7r8Ij8e4ypxuJ58AJQhcQ","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"- Posible adición de agentes anti-LMC no-ITQ (hidroxiurea, omacetaxina, azacitidina, decitabina, citarabina)","guid":"glA7a-ggIYV8elfszGYW9g","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"0","text":"## MONITORIZACIÓN Y\\NRESPUESTA AL TRATAMIENTO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"- Puntos de\\Nreferencia\\Nimportantes:","guid":"sXAxxFfIEltBn9zD-xXVFQ","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"- BCR::ABL1 ≤10% a los 3 meses","guid":"GGQEvczb-Vsvp7QT036XPQ","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"59","text":"- Respuesta citogenética completa (RCC)","guid":"oXDfCu2qIw9FPjZ3TEuYaQ","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"59","text":"- Respuesta molecular mayor (RMM)","guid":"RO2y8Q4nMFNdPJaHxQqNyw","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"59","text":"- Respuesta molecular profunda (RMP)","guid":"RwujflCknamnVdjWb2JZZA","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"58","text":"- Frecuencia de\\Nmonitorización:","guid":"LL_iKG5KLEzwbIixL61GVA","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"- Primer año: PCR en sangre periférica cada 3 meses","guid":"B-_5hS9zVtBglOfbj27BOA","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"- Con RMM confirmada: monitorización cada 6 meses","guid":"peOBq-ahpUkYtkgv3sRTyQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"0","text":"## RESISTENCIA A ITQ","guid":"","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"- Definida como BCR::ABL1 >1% después de 12 meses","guid":"jxklIy6UE8tg_t8gyHkF4Q","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"- Mutaciones en dominio quinasa de BCR::ABL1","guid":"bDdaE9qJ7gpCN4BbGXin6Q","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"- Análisis de mutaciones guía elección de terapia subsecuente","guid":"0_nOQVeQrjntOR7RQktXnA","children":[]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"0","text":"## DISCONTINUACIÓN\\NDEL TRATAMIENTO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"- Posible en pacientes con respuesta molecular profunda duradera","guid":"N2_ew0zZYrisbCkNgOYaaQ","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"71","text":"- Tasa de remisión libre de tratamiento: 40-50%","guid":"eTpk0hmiEq7mcthebjFL3Q","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"71","text":"- Factores\\Nfavorables:","guid":"XpkyEoLBJ2CnR3nEQNRxRw","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"- RMP mantenida por ≥4-5 años","guid":"7WtnnRciukvnkqM1V0rHig","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"74","text":"- Tratamiento con ITQ por ≥6-7 años","guid":"KUo9KE2dKx-Gi4_HI9n8iw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"0","text":"## LMC EN FASE\\NAVANZADA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"- Fase acelerada/blástica: peor pronóstico","guid":"mOCdWxWdLTzGZMjfFoWFjQ","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"77","text":"- Opciones de\\Ntratamiento:","guid":"3OI6hipi009Cv_zKR7UDSw","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"- Combinación ITQ con quimioterapia","guid":"xIFPlk7zJvzSXZT6cdeY3Q","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"- Seguido por trasplante alogénico","guid":"C3Yj7kqljdOf-roAwPJMEg","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"77","text":"- Supervivencia a largo plazo en FB: 10-20%","guid":"65ZqPcuE_L5fkktXyk1lkg","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":82,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Hematología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Hematología","filename":"Paper. Leucemia mieloide crónica-2025-1","id":"map_1077","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Paper. Leucemia mieloide crónica-2025-1"}